title: Kaijin Kaihatsu-bu no Kuroitsu-san
synopsis: Touka Kuroizu is a research assistant who belongs to the Monster Development Department of the evil organization Agastia. However, the enemy she has to fight right now isn't the heroes of justice, but her boss.
staff: [['Saitou, Hisashi', ['Director']], ['Takayama, Katsuhiko', ['Series Composition']], ['Morimae, Kazuya', ['Character Design']], ['Mizusaki, Hiroaki', ['Original Creator']]]
